    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a structurally sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit showcases exceptional mechanical health with a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously timed for optimal valve overlap. The individual throttle bodies (ITBs) provide instantaneous transient throttle response, paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The rear subframe\u2014a known focal point for this chassis\u2014has been inspected and reinforced to ensure torsional rigidity under heavy lateral loads. It retains the factory-spec variable M differential lock for superior traction exiting corners. While the exterior reflects its status as a driven enthusiast car, the suspension geometry remains true, and the engine's compression across all six cylinders is within factory tolerances. A purist\u2019s spec focused on kinetic performance and tactile feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
